# RTL in this project

For **writing, reviewing, or refactoring** Verilog (`.v`, `.vh`) or SystemVerilog (`.sv`, `.svh`) in matched files, invoke **`@rtl-design`** in Agent chat.

For **SDC** use **`@sdc`**. For **timing analysis / STA reports** use **`@timing-analysis`**. Type **`@help`** to list all invokes.

Match the **dialect and style** of the surrounding files in this project.

Install the [rtl-design-agent](https://github.com/YOURORG/rtl-design-agent) repo (or open it) so `docs/standards/` is available to the agent.
